Description of Calculator
November 9, 2023
1 Introduction
This document provides a brief overview of a Java program named Calculator
which implements a basic calculator with additional functionalities for unit conversion and matrix operations.
2 Basic Calculator Operations
The calculator program offers the following basic operations:
• Addition
• Subtraction
• Multiplication
• Division
Users can choose these operations through a menu system.
3 Unit Conversion
The program also includes a unit conversion feature. Users can convert:
• Feet to Meters
• Miles to Kilometers
4 Matrix Operations
Additionally, the calculator program supports matrix operations, specifically:
• Matrix Addition
• Matrix Subtraction
Users can perform these operations on predefined 2x2 matrices.
1
5 Conclusion
The Calculator program provides a versatile tool for performing basic calculations, unit conversions, and matrix operations. It offers a user-friendly interface
through a text-based menu system.
